code: public boolean matches(Class<?> type) {     if (type == null) {         return false.     }     for (Class<? extends Annotation> annotation : annotations) {         if (ObjectHelper.hasAnnotation(type, annotation, checkMetaAnnotations)) {             return true.         }     }     return false. }
